The Bon-Ton - Wikipedia





















 






The Bon-Ton

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about a department store. For other uses, see Bon Ton.

The Bon-Ton Stores, Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: BONT


Industry
Retail


Founded
1898


Headquarters
York, Pennsylvania, and Milwaukee, Wisconsin U.S.



Number of locations

267 (Q3 2016)[1]



Key people

Kathy Bufano President & CEO
